data.description: Introducing an exquisite home in the prestigious Los Lomas subdivision. Situated on 1.51-acre lot, this property offers a truly exceptional living experience. 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, this home is designed with comfort and elegance in mind. The open concept floor plan creates a seamless flow between the main living areas, making it perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with family. With two spacious living areas, there is ample room for relaxation and entertainment, plus a bonus room provides a versatile space whether it be a home office, media room, or fitness center. Also featuring RV parking, catering to those with a sense of adventure and a love for exploring the open road. Immerse yourself in breathtaking 360-degree views, offering a panoramic vista of the natural Alamogordo beauty. Whether it's the majestic mountains or stunning sunsets, this home provides an ever-changing backdrop that will leave you in awe.  Schedule your private tour today!
